 implementation eq
parameters
	real i = 60.0 {};				// gearbox ratio
equations
	p_out.T = p_in.T*i;
	p_out.omega = p_in.omega/i;
                     implementation_end;
specification_end;
				specification 'Lossy'
description '<Description><Version>4.0</Version><IsMainModel>1</IsMainModel><KeepParameterValues>False</KeepParameterValues>
   <LibraryPath>Iconic Diagrams\Mechanical\Rotation\Gears\Transmission.emx</LibraryPath>
